sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant LS as Language Server (snyk-ls)
    participant LC as SnykExtendedLanguageClient<br/>(@JsonNotification "$/snyk.treeView")
    participant TV as SnykToolView (ViewPart)
    participant TBH as TreeViewBrowserHandler
    participant B as SWT Browser
    participant JS as tree.js (in Browser)

    Note over LS: Scan completes →<br/>TreeBuilder renders HTML →<br/>TreeScanStateEmitter sends notification
    LS->>LC: $/snyk.treeView { treeViewHtml, totalIssues }
    LC->>TV: updateTreeViewHtml(html)  [SWT thread via Display.asyncExec]
    TV->>TBH: setHtml(html)
    TBH->>TBH: prepend EclipseThemeCssProvider.css(display)
    TBH->>B: browser.setText(themedHtml)
    B->>JS: parse, init UI
    Note over JS: ExecuteCommandBridge already injected:<br/>window.__ideExecuteCommand__ available
